{"tid":1924342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"咁多國家中招，唯獨中國冇宣布進入緊急狀態，點解？","createTime":"2020-03-13T15:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T17:34:18.000Z","uid":48040,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"624f4de1a15af43ed497a7f5c0a86301dacba8d1","tid":1924342,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:34:37.000Z","msg":"因為呢個國家冇法治。<br />\n所謂緊急狀態，即係政府可以為了瘟疫或戰爭的特殊需要，為了公眾利益，而暫時限制人身自由以及徵用私人物資。<br />\n其他國家假如要限制人身自由、調用民間資源等等，<br />\n必須要按照憲法，由政府宣布進入緊急狀態，然後才可以實施緊急狀態下的法律。<br />\n疫情結束，亦會立即宣布解除緊急狀態，公民恢復人身自由，以及私有財產權。<br />\n<br />\n中國呢？其實無論有冇疫情，都冇人身自由及財產權。<br />\n所以中國根本冇必要宣布緊急狀態。<br />\n或者話，從1949年建國起，呢個國家一直都係處於緊急狀態之中。"},{"pid":"fce8d513b10fdbcab4a6a803abcac031dbccbbef","tid":1924342,"uid":8745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"戰時管理"},{"pid":"39f6ba6d643d2918c258b0c6de1c52c505acaf7b","tid":1924342,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"聽日爆炸案被打到入廠手足案件會上庭，跪求聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1924327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1924327</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0cf275d5814dcc0b05cf579f25f53e48b918a5a9","tid":1924342,"uid":50328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33e4c30453be12a399d916f2ff6eabbf25228562","tid":1924342,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:37:14.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"190df1c4dd8925b2f817cf69d52ca7c0593bf25a","tid":1924342,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">六四戒嚴算係破例</span>"},{"pid":"a0abf6e7341391115c632f08eabe522fa8069028","tid":1924342,"uid":8478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"緊急狀態=大屠殺進行中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2e725e59ab3890c76758dfc673b